      • generate

        public void generate()
        Fetch all relevant data from database and process them to get a list of largest rise and fall for each name. If names no not appear in a year of a dataset after its discovery, the year for said name will be ignored e.g. if David appeared in 2000 but not in 2001 for said dataset, David's Name Object will not be updated. Note that the years are ranked using Standard Competition Ranking. The output is stored in the parent Superclass ReportLog variable oReport and oHTML for the controller to fetch and output.

      • getResults

        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.Vector<java.lang.String>> getResults()
        Returns:
        HashMap of Column (String) to Vector of (entries String) for the Console to fetch the results of the output/ It will show all Names with the largest increase in popularity or largest fall in popularity. Note that if a name has multiple Trends with the largest increase in popularity or fall in popularity, only the most recent trend will be listed
